title: Zojirushi Home Bakery Virtuoso® Breadmaker BB-PAC20
description:
From novice to expert, now any home baker can take advantage of our most technologically advanced breadmaker, the Zojirushi Home Bakery Virtuoso® Breadmaker BB-PAC20. It is loaded with menu settings like the special Gluten Free course, and features a built in revolutionary heating element that bakes perfect bread every time. With options for the ultimate in versatility, anyone can be a master baker.

Abt is a proud authorized retailer of the Zojirushi Home Bakery Virtuoso Breadmaker - BBPAC20. Shop for the Zojirushi Home Bakery Virtuoso Breadmaker, as well as the full line of Zojirushi Kitchen Appliances at Abt today!
